703553f-a.title: Brooklyn: Church Avenue - 48th Street (East)
703553f-a.text:
Church Ave., at the N.E. corner of East 48th Street, showing Public School No. 135, which was rased in 1926. In the foreground, is the Church
Ave., Trolley Line. Note the unfinished Street.
March 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
